    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a quintessential analog driver\u2019s machine. Powered by the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system, this engine pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity under lateral load. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise gates, sending power to the rear wheels via the factory limited-slip differential. Suspension remains composed with refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the car's legendary 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. While the aesthetic reflects its age and driver-focused history, the powertrain and drivetrain are dialed in for peak performance. A visceral, high-induction-note experience for the serious enthusiast.",
