    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s still in really solid shape and ready for its next adventure. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable, well-cared-for ride that still looks great on the road. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it, and I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the basics so you can just hop in and go. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I\u2019d love for it to find a new home where it'll be appreciated! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
