    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a broad, linear torque curve. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal power delivery to the rear wheels. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS service. The chassis remains composed with a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup, currently fitted with refreshed bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are dialed in for peak performance, offering a visceral, analog driving experience that remains the benchmark for the M-division.",
